TextEng: The High Captains are killin' each other, they are. Don't you be one to get in their way.
Text: 대선장들이 서로 죽이고 있다네. 그 사이에 끼어들진 말라고.

TextEng: The Bloody Hands came an' burned down my home... took everything I had. May the gods damn them all!
Text: 피묻은 손 놈들이 와서 내 집을 불태웠어... 가진 거 다 빼앗겼지. 신들이 그놈들을 저주하길!

TextEng: Don't let anyone hear ye talk about the High Captains. Ye'll wind up dead, ye will.
Text: 대선장들 얘기하는 거 아무한테도 들키지 마. 죽을 수도 있어.

TextEng: What? Were ye robbed of all yer clothing by the soldiers?
Text: 뭐? 병사들한테 옷을 전부 털린 건가?

TextEng: Put some clothes on, <man/woman>. Ye're not in the brothel, are ye?
Text: 옷 좀 입어, 이 <man/woman>아. 여긴 창관이 아니라고?

TextEng: Did ye forget something, <lad/lass>? Like clothes, mayhap?
Text: 뭔가 잊은 거 없어, <lad/lass>? 옷이라든가?

TextEng: Ach, ye were fighting, I see. Did the monsters outside get to ye?
Text: 아, 싸웠구만. 바깥 괴물들한테 당한 거야?

TextEng: Maybe ye should see someone 'bout them nasty cuts of yours.
Text: 그 지저분한 상처들 누구한테 좀 보이는 게 좋겠어.

TextEng: That must've been some tussle you were in. Most folks'd be dead in yer shoes.
Text: 엄청난 싸움이었나 보네. 대부분은 그 꼴이면 죽었을 거야.

TextEng: I've got a cousin who were slow-witted like ye. He's dead, now.
Text: 나한테도 너처럼 머리 나쁜 사촌이 있었어. 이제 죽었지만.

TextEng: Best a simple <man/woman> like yerself keep off the streets.
Text: 너처럼 단순한 <man/woman>은 거리에 안 나가는 게 좋아.

TextEng: Don't go into the streets, <lad/lass>. It be dangerous. Ye know that word? Danger?
Text: 거리에 나가지 마, <lad/lass>. 위험하거든. 그 말 알아? 위험?

TextEng: I've seen enough weapons being waved about. Put yers away.
Text: 무기 휘두르는 거 충분히 봤어. 네 것도 치워.

TextEng: Stop shakin' that about. Ye're makin' me nervous.
Text: 그거 흔드는 거 그만해. 불안하잖아.

TextEng: People are scared enough here as it is. Put that away.
Text: 사람들이 이미 겁에 질려 있어. 그거 치워.

TextEng: Don't see too much holy folk 'round Luskan.
Text: 러스칸에서 성직자는 별로 못 보거든.

TextEng: Maybe prayin's what we should be doing. Luskan's gone to hell, it seems.
Text: 기도나 해야 할 것 같아. 러스칸이 지옥이 됐으니.

TextEng: You're a holy <man/woman>, ain't ye? Ye come to help us?
Text: 성직자시군요? 우릴 도우러 온 건가요?

TextEng: Lotta good yer magicks do us. Bloody Brotherhood is behind all o' this, I swear.
Text: 네 마법이 뭔 소용이야. 이 모든 게 빌어먹을 결사단 짓이라니까.

TextEng: Ye're not part of the Arcane Brotherhood, are ye?
Text: 혹시 비전 결사단 소속은 아니지?

TextEng: Ye should go back to the Host Tower. We don't need yer kind 'round here.
Text: 중심탑으로 돌아가. 여기선 네 부류가 필요 없어.

TextEng: Ye're a might fine-lookin' lass. Ye come from Bela's, aye?
Text: 참 예쁜 아가씨네. 벨라네에서 왔어?

TextEng: It's good to know there's still some fine women who ain't been killed.
Text: 아직 죽지 않은 예쁜 여자가 있다니 다행이네.

TextEng: Maybe I could buy ye a drink, lass?
Text: 술 한잔 사줘도 될까, 아가씨?

TextEng: The Arcane Brotherhood is behind all o' this... they've risen up zombies and werewolves and are tryin' to kill us all!
Text: 비전 결사단이 이 모든 일의 배후야... 좀비랑 늑대인간을 일으켜서 우릴 다 죽이려 하고 있어!

TextEng: If I were you, friend, I'd stay off the streets. Until this is over, none o' us are safe.
Text: 나라면, 친구, 거리에 안 나갈 거야. 이게 끝날 때까지 누구도 안전하지 않아.

TextEng: I hear some of the pirate crews blockaded the Mirabar trade district once the ports were closed.
Text: 항구가 폐쇄되자 해적 패거리 일부가 미라바르 무역 지구를 봉쇄했다고 들었어.

TextEng: The High Captains have gone mad! They've put monsters in their armies and are going to kill each other while Luskan suffers!
Text: 대선장들이 미쳤어! 군대에 괴물을 넣고 러스칸이 고통받는 동안 서로 죽이려 하고 있다고!

TextEng: What? Driven out of your home by rampaging guardsmen, were you? Join the club... nobody's stopping these madmen.
Text: 뭐? 날뛰는 경비병들한테 집에서 쫓겨났어? 우리도 마찬가지야... 이 미친놈들을 막을 사람이 없어.

TextEng: Get away from me, you! I've had me fill o' assassins and thieves stalking the streets!
Text: 저리 가! 거리를 배회하는 암살자랑 도둑은 질렸다고!

TextEng: Ye must be one of them Uthgardt peoples, aye?
Text: 우스가르트 사람인가 보네, 그렇지?

TextEng: City's closed off, an' somehow ye barbarian types still find yer way in.
Text: 도시가 봉쇄됐는데 어떻게든 야만인들은 들어오는구만.

TextEng: Careful, now. Big <man/woman> like yerself will be snatched up by the soldiers in a second.
Text: 조심해. 너처럼 덩치 큰 <man/woman>은 금방 병사들한테 붙잡혀.

TextEng: We don't welcome ye <race> folk in Luskan, much.
Text: 러스칸에선 <race> 종족을 별로 환영 안 해.

TextEng: Better not go out in the street, you. They kills any <race> kind on sight.
Text: 거리에 나가지 마. <race>는 보이는 대로 죽인다고.

TextEng: I saw one of the Bloody Hand killin' some <race> travelers just yesterday.
Text: 어제 피묻은 손 놈 하나가 <race> 여행자들을 죽이는 거 봤어.
